To that end, though, my critique of Substack is the same one I have always =
had: a lack of honesty, not just with writers, but themselves. I wrote in a=
n Update last year ( https://stratechery.com/2022/substack-launches-app-sub=
stack-and-the-four-bens-in-app-purchase-and-the-substack-bundle/?access_tok=
